  "keyFeatures": [
    "CLI for OpenAI GPT Image 2 text-to-image generation and reference-image editing",
    "Agentic skill for Claude Code, Codex, and other skill-capable agent runtimes",
    "162-prompt curated gallery organized into 30+ categories",
    "Support for multi-reference edits and alpha-channel mask inpainting",
    "Quality/budget knob (low/medium/high) for cost-conscious generation",
    "Split Reference Gallery Atlas for context-efficient agent usage",
    "Full parameter coverage: size, quality, format, compression, background, moderation"
